    "is_free": true,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>OUT OF BOUNDS</strong> is a first-person survival sandbox set in the Backrooms. Will you survive long enough to find an exit, or will you perish to the dangers lurking in this never-ending nightmare?</p><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3089390/extras/9106ab260ab88885540e42c376b739cd.avif?t=1769965690\" alt=\"Fully Interactable Levels\" width=1560 height=975 /></span><br><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore a variety of levels with unique resources and dangers. <br>Every object can be moved around with physics or can be interacted with; If you see it, you can do something with it.</p><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3089390/extras/45575b47010a3318264539637f64d909.avif?t=1769965690\" alt=\"Extensive Tech Tree and Crafting\" width=1560 height=975 /></span><br><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Various crafting recipes for you to discover and unlock through a vast tech tree.<br>Bandages, makeshift weapons, electrical and mechanical components and parts. Every recipe has its purpose.</p><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3089390/extras/a459e82df1f95260bce6abc503a1d4c5.avif?t=1769965690\" alt=\"Build a Base With Anything\" width=1560 height=975 /></span><br><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Almost every object can be moved around freely and can be anchored and fixed in place.<br>Make a base to store your resources and keep all your working stations, while staying safe from the dangers lurking in the dark.</p><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3089390/extras/ac9e200f5d810f1f65120bacc59c8d22.avif?t=1769965690\" alt=\"Survive With Friends\" width=1560 height=975 /></span><br><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Bring your friends to help you fight against the odds in this twisted reality.<br>Work together to gather resources and food, explore and build your fortress.</p>",
